{"tid":1693755,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得而家罷工搞唔成，係每個人對其他人冇信心，驚最後自己係少數罷工既人。","createTime":"2019-11-04T19:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T03:22:50.000Z","uid":136412,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a97e9af9a70caea1b12cf5f98d650197a95f28da","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:13:56.000Z","msg":"我覺得要用多d時間，各行各業要搞個罷工組織。收集願意罷工罷足一星期既人數，再係達到一個數量先公佈罷工細節，罷工完左後跟進揪後算算帳既公司，放入民間懲罰名單。<br />\n罷工既話如果銀行業既內部，運輸業，同政府部門先係最重要。<br />\n我認為唯有做到咁detail，罷工先有可能成功。"},{"pid":"5e10e4320df61b4b377797d8a418f577546f16e7","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:14:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cbf3d9df5bc78aa35e3d19cf7e8f9cb25b4e574","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:15:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5dbca9d88dad2e0ae332c5bff7563e8ea3b3df0","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:16:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d311f977719d753c55884eb1953ce4ef235a0bef","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:18:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e80d174cad541a2246e07cacd413e848deceba8","tid":1693755,"uid":271973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:19:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54598b327b1a1db6c8c9fb6bbd6e36015b79232e","tid":1693755,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:20:55.000Z","msg":"點解九月罷工搞唔成？唔係因為文宣唔夠，係因為八五罷工之後，中共出招，職場篤灰之風蔓延，航空界唔敢再罷。<br />\n<br />\n咁可以點做？文宣解決唔到嘅問題，要由真人響office度解決！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ej7C2jE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fej7C2jE.jpg&h=8241dc37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【五個步驟&mdash;&mdash;組織職場手足】<br />\n<br />\n運動發展到今日，大家都明白我哋係要打持久戰，同呢個腐敗嘅政權鬥長命，所以我哋更加要擴大自己嘅力量，團結我哋嘅自己人﹗嚟緊呢個星期會同大家分享吓，點樣組織自己友嘅具體方法，希望大家都可以係自己職場運用啦﹗<br />\n<br />\n1) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">辨認手足</span>: 戴口罩返工、有香港鎖匙扣、有和你返工同快閃嘅活動日子都遲返、留意公司或者同事群組有冇嘢講抗爭議題<br />\n<br />\n2)<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 開群組</span>：交流資訊如果有興趣嘅人都可以加入(不過要提防管理層同二五仔)<br />\n<br />\n3) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">從簡單行動開始</span>：戴口罩、貼貼紙memo、Airdrop文宣等<br />\n<br />\n4) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">進一步組織</span>：組團快閃、約埋去集會、一齊諗點支援運動，另外亦要了解各人就罷工等不同升級行動嘅看法<br />\n<br />\n5) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">組織工會</span>：令自己更有牙力，除咗政治表態，亦關注行業權益，增加職場話語權！"},{"pid":"a2da189a8f51e38f8bd5af732673ac11b5d63844","tid":1693755,"uid":52686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:23:38.000Z","msg":"好提議 好多時真係驚得自己一個罷"},{"pid":"610d153d198be40cac3e3f3306c6ac4278e5afe5","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:35:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c9830237812bfbcaec1104e08a38ed0ecaec3728","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:37:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c49f95e441cd58da599b84e921ed9ad31da1d3d3","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:53:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1215eef5dc6924362d71da6496058c6d8ce79953","tid":1693755,"uid":200298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T19:55:30.000Z","msg":"咁只要令其他人返唔到工就得啦。<br />\n<br />\n[行動Post] 真正End Game方法 - 三罷全面抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691829</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac22ab47848721ba3f9f6d729ccd6bd6e2b67df8","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:40:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"71ce11a391e7cfd04f48fc989196aa714e6d5a10","tid":1693755,"uid":136412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"39eb036711f3f886e9e3a4c494b004f748cccfc1","tid":1693755,"uid":320078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:22:50.000Z","msg":"唔好再講再賴咩某行業罷最有用啦<br />\n根本就係藉口想自己唔罷<br />\n要罷就所有行業都罷, 知唔知咩叫齊上齊落呀"}]}